description: AUBURN, Ala. â€“ No. 14 Auburn women's tennis came through with a comeback for the ages, rallying from a 3-1 deficit with wins on all three remaining courts to secure a 4-3 win over No. 33 Georgia Tech, clinching a spot in the NCAA Round of 16 for the third time in program history.
